504
00:21:57,719 --> 00:21:58,920
Suddenly it swung open.

505
00:21:58,920 --> 00:22:00,479
Then he popped his head out.

506
00:22:00,747 --> 00:22:04,400
(Earlier tonight)

507
00:22:04,400 --> 00:22:05,520
I was about to knock.

508
00:22:05,520 --> 00:22:06,599
And you just opened up.

509
00:22:08,439 --> 00:22:10,040
Nothing, just checking on you.

510
00:22:10,040 --> 00:22:10,959
I was asleep just now.

511
00:22:11,599 --> 00:22:12,160
Keep resting.

512
00:22:45,079 --> 00:22:46,640
