513
00:22:46,640 --> 00:22:47,359
I can try again, right?

514
00:22:49,680 --> 00:22:50,439
You can go.

515
00:22:51,880 --> 00:22:53,000
You're out.

516
00:22:53,599 --> 00:22:54,319
You can go.

517
00:22:55,079 --> 00:22:56,239
Lost your chance.

518
00:23:10,063 --> 00:23:13,040
(Xu Lvyang: Slow to catch on like me)

519
00:23:13,040 --> 00:23:14,599
Liu's Moments is

520
00:23:14,599 --> 00:23:16,959
"Slow to catch on like me."

521
00:23:16,959 --> 00:23:17,880
