526
00:23:26,680 --> 00:23:27,800
"Slow to catch on like me."

527
00:23:29,160 --> 00:23:30,839
It's how I feel right now.

528
00:23:30,839 --> 00:23:31,479
It's like,

529
00:23:33,119 --> 00:23:34,880
Ling Lizheng's feelings,

530
00:23:35,839 --> 00:23:37,239
Zhou Youling's feelings,

531
00:23:37,800 --> 00:23:38,760
or BK's feelings.

532
00:23:38,760 --> 00:23:40,199
I'm actually slow to catch on.

533
00:23:41,319 --> 00:23:43,719
I didn't expect Ling Lizheng

534
00:23:44,599 --> 00:23:48,640
to pick me up at the gate

535
00:23:48,640 --> 00:23:49,520
