536
00:23:50,760 --> 00:23:51,839
Hello.

537
00:23:51,839 --> 00:23:53,640
How did you know I was coming back?

538
00:23:53,640 --> 00:23:54,920
I was passing by

539
00:23:54,920 --> 00:23:55,439
