540
00:23:55,439 --> 00:23:57,119
You came out for a walk?

541
00:23:57,119 --> 00:23:57,359
Yeah.

542
00:23:57,959 --> 00:23:59,959
I didn't expect Zhou Youling

543
00:24:00,520 --> 00:24:01,640
to open the door

544
00:24:01,640 --> 00:24:03,400
