549
00:24:32,479 --> 00:24:34,160
I need some fresh air.

550
00:24:34,719 --> 00:24:35,359
Together.

551
00:24:35,839 --> 00:24:36,680
Come on, baby.

552
00:24:40,160 --> 00:24:41,599
Do you want to find someone
who likes you more,

553
00:24:41,599 --> 00:24:42,599
or someone you like more?

554
00:24:43,479 --> 00:24:44,959
It has to be someone I like.

555
00:24:45,439 --> 00:24:46,760
Even if someone likes me a lot,

556
00:24:46,760 --> 00:24:47,400
