559
00:24:49,959 --> 00:24:50,760
(Clear-minded)

560
00:24:50,760 --> 00:24:51,439
If you like someone,

561
00:24:51,439 --> 00:24:52,119
will you always

562
00:24:52,119 --> 00:24:53,800
