563
00:24:53,800 --> 00:24:54,880
Or is it just

564
00:24:54,880 --> 00:24:55,359
at the beginning?

565
00:24:56,760 --> 00:24:57,640
I think

566
00:24:58,119 --> 00:24:59,760
if I truly like someone,

567
00:24:59,760 --> 00:25:00,760
that feeling

568
00:25:00,760 --> 00:25:02,520
won't fade away.

569
00:25:02,520 --> 00:25:03,319
But if

570
00:25:03,319 --> 00:25:04,239
I liked him

571
00:25:04,239 --> 00:25:05,359
and we didn't make it,

572
00:25:05,359 --> 00:25:06,040
or

573
00:25:06,040 --> 00:25:07,400
