574
00:25:07,400 --> 00:25:09,520
my feelings could be gone very soon.

575
00:25:09,520 --> 00:25:11,160
It depends on his response.

576
00:25:11,160 --> 00:25:11,800
Yeah.

577
00:25:11,800 --> 00:25:13,000
I need responses

578
00:25:13,000 --> 00:25:15,160
to sustain a relationship.

579
00:25:15,160 --> 00:25:16,160
It has to be in sync.

580
00:25:16,160 --> 00:25:17,280
You take a step,

581
00:25:17,280 --> 00:25:17,719
I take a step.

582
00:25:17,719 --> 00:25:18,239
Yeah.

583
00:25:18,719 --> 00:25:19,680
That's crucial.

584
00:25:19,680 --> 00:25:20,959
Or it's just unrequited love.

585
00:25:20,959 --> 00:25:21,439
One-sided.

586
00:25:21,439 --> 00:25:22,000
Yeah.

587
00:25:22,479 --> 00:25:23,079
Everyone

588
00:25:23,079 --> 00:25:25,959
