their own rhythm and bottom line.

589
00:25:25,959 --> 00:25:26,719
If you feel

590
00:25:26,719 --> 00:25:28,040
you're willing to move forward,

591
00:25:28,040 --> 00:25:28,920
then go ahead.

592
00:25:28,920 --> 00:25:29,439
But if

593
00:25:29,439 --> 00:25:30,640
you've reached your limit,

594
00:25:30,640 --> 00:25:31,599
then stop.

595
00:25:31,599 --> 00:25:33,040
That's all fine.

596
00:25:34,079 --> 00:25:36,000
But relationships are complicated.

597
00:25:36,000 --> 00:25:38,800
We may encounter many things
that wear us down.

598
00:25:40,040 --> 00:25:40,439
Yeah.

599
00:25:41,599 --> 00:25:43,199
Especially,

600
00:25:43,199 --> 00:25:44,520
we're all adults.

601
00:25:44,520 --> 00:25:45,680
There are many things

602
00:25:45,680 --> 00:25:47,119
to think about.

603
00:25:47,760 --> 00:25:48,119
Yeah.

604
00:25:48,719 --> 00:25:50,359
You may want someone idealistic

605
00:25:50,359 --> 00:25:50,920
while trying

606
00:25:50,920 --> 00:25:52,920
to keep it down to earth.

607
00:25:53,640 --> 00:25:54,560
It's really hard.

608
00:25:56,560 --> 00:25:57,119
Yeah.

609
00:25:57,520 --> 00:26:00,520
Before I turned thirty,

610
00:26:00,520 --> 00:26:01,119
I didn't even

611
00:26:01,119 --> 00:26:01,880
think about

612
00:26:01,880 --> 00:26:03,280
having kids and stuff.

613
00:26:03,839 --> 00:26:05,599
But now at thirty-three,

614
00:26:05,599 --> 00:26:07,239
I think I'm moving

615
00:26:08,040 --> 00:26:09,359
towards that direction.

616
00:26:10,319 --> 00:26:11,000
Yeah.

617
00:26:11,000 --> 00:26:12,599
So would you want a family?

618
00:26:13,680 --> 00:26:15,000
I'm not against it.

619
00:26:15,640 --> 00:26:17,359
I used to think

620
00:26:17,359 --> 00:26:18,520
I didn't really need it.

621
00:26:18,520 --> 00:26:19,359
But now I think

622
00:26:19,359 --> 00:26:21,319
I'm open to the possibility.

623
00:26:21,319 --> 00:26:21,959
And I think

624
00:26:21,959 --> 00:26:23,640
I'm starting to want it

625
00:26:23,640 --> 00:26:24,439
because

626
00:26:24,959 --> 00:26:26,400
I've figured out...

627
00:26:26,959 --> 00:26:28,400
What you want in life.

628
00:26:28,400 --> 00:26:28,640
Yeah.

629
00:26:28,640 --> 00:26:29,719
Or rather, I've figured out

630
00:26:29,719 --> 00:26:30,920
what I need to give

631
00:26:30,920 --> 00:26:31,920
to have a family.

632
00:26:33,520 --> 00:26:34,680
If I want a family,

633
00:26:34,680 --> 00:26:35,359
I might have to

634
00:26:35,359 --> 00:26:36,560
devote a lot of time

635
00:26:36,560 --> 00:26:37,760
and energy.

636
00:26:37,760 --> 00:26:38,479
Work.

637
00:26:38,479 --> 00:26:39,239
Yeah.

638
00:26:39,239 --> 00:26:39,920
And everything.

639
00:26:39,920 --> 00:26:41,719
Am I willing to do so?

640
00:26:41,719 --> 00:26:42,920
Is it balanced?

641
00:26:42,920 --> 00:26:43,640
Yeah.

642
00:26:43,640 --> 00:26:44,880
Now I'm willing to do so.

643
00:26:45,319 --> 00:26:47,160
So I think I can try

644
00:26:47,160 --> 00:26:48,359
to start a family.

645
00:26:48,880 --> 00:26:50,119
This is the best part

646
00:26:50,119 --> 00:26:51,880
about

647
00:26:51,880 --> 00:26:52,800
being in your thirties.

648
00:26:52,800 --> 00:26:54,560
You've figured out

649
00:26:54,560 --> 00:26:55,199
what you want.

650
00:26:55,199 --> 00:26:56,079
(Clear-headed)
Yeah.

651
00:27:06,784 --> 00:27:08,416
How come this face
is packed like sardines?

652
00:27:09,714 --> 00:27:11,072
I vote for Park Hae-jin.

653
00:27:11,072 --> 00:27:12,785
I only recognize my big brother.

654
00:27:12,785 --> 00:27:14,197
Makes me look like I have no EQ.

655
00:27:14,688 --> 00:27:15,744
Cut.

656
00:27:17,293 --> 00:27:18,048
Like this.

657
00:27:19,860 --> 00:27:20,829
Okay.

658
00:27:22,186 --> 00:27:23,208
Okay.

659
00:27:23,232 --> 00:27:25,024
A teacher with a student in class.

660
00:27:25,042 --> 00:27:26,400
Preschool teacher.

661
00:27:26,400 --> 00:27:27,296
Have a seat.
